   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Response to Repatriated Returnees in Laghman Province of Afghanistan.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">By implementing the above mentioned activities the returnees life will be saving, they will be able to survive during winter cold season.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
